steps.description:
There is a tricky situation that I don't see discussed in [the current RFC](https://github.com/opentofu/opentofu/blob/0cc4301cd51bf3ef1de4d87edfef2ab81cb678b8/rfc/20240513-static-evaluation-providers.md). :thinking: 

Consider the following configuration:

```hcl
variable "regions" {
  type =
```yaml
provider "aws" {
  region = "eu-central-1"
  alias  = "x1"
}

provider "aws" {
  region = "eu-west-1"
  alias  = "x2"
}



resource "aws_resource" "x1" {
  provider = aws.x1
}

resource "aws_resource" "x2" {
  provider = aws.x2
}
```

